text = "CONGRATULATIONS!

YOU HAVE BEEN HIRED AS AN INDEPENDENT DELIVERY CONTRACTOR FOR SWIFTSHIP LOGISTICS.

1. 1 CONTRACTOR RESPONSIBILITIES

- DELIVER PACKAGES [color=2574e4]SAFELY[/color].
- RESPECT DELIVERY [color=de7915]DEADLINES[/color].
- AVOID DAMAGING COMPANY PROPERTY.

1.2 EARNINGS

- DAMAGED [color=2574e4]FRAGILE[/color] PACKAGES MAY REDUCE EARNINGS.
- LATE [color=de7915]URGENT[/color] DELIVERIES MAY REDUCE EARNINGS.
- FAILURE TO MAINTAIN YOUR VEHICLE MAY IMPACT PERFORMANCE.

1.3 COMPENSATION

THE CONTRACTOR SHALL RECEIVE COMPENSATION FOR EACH SUCCESSFULLY COMPLETED DELIVERY."
fit_content = true

