text = "1.4 VEHICLE MAINTENANCE

THE CONTRACTOR IS SOLELY RESPONSIBLE FOR THE MAINTENANCE, REPAIR, AND OPERATING CONDITION OF THEIR VEHICLE.

ROUTINE MAINTENANCE COSTS, REPAIRS, REPLACEMENT PARTS, AND ALL ASSOCIATED EXPENSES SHALL BE BORNE ENTIRELY BY THE CONTRACTOR.

THE COMPANY ASSUMES NO RESPONSIBILITY FOR MECHANICAL FAILURES RESULTING FROM INSUFFICIENT MAINTENANCE.


BY SIGNING BELOW, THE CONTRACTOR ACKNOWLEDGES THAT THEY HAVE READ, UNDERSTOOD, AND ACCEPTED THE TERMS OF THIS AGREEMENT."
